description: How are people feeling in Tokyo? What are happy people saying? We Feel Fine is an exploration of human emotion on a global scale. No matter where we are, who we are or how we live, we all feel. Built off of the compelling We Feel Fine project http://wefeelfine.org/
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask we feel fine what are people feeling?
How do people feel in Tokyo?
name: We Feel Fine
shortDescription: Listen to real sentiments from across the globe and see beauty in the everyday ups and downs of life.
